reviews.review_text:
Enjoyable Recording Had a great time listening to this. Since last year, China Doll has become one of my favorites for Dead Suites, and it sounds great coming from the Playing In the Band jam. The China Doll has a particular rushed quality that I really liked, and the crowd's receptiveness to (you know the spot) in China Doll was awesome. They also responded very well to Wharf Rat's "'nother fucker's crime." 
The tape had a really enjoyable quality. Loved the performance, and thanks for posting this.
